<reference id="enum_watermarkfitmode">
    <title><ph keyref="WATERMARK_FIT_MODE"/></title>
    <shortdesc id="short"><ph id="shortdesc">The adaptation mode of the watermark.</ph></shortdesc>
    <refbody>
        <section id="parameters">
            <title>Enumerator</title>
            <parml>
            <plentry>
                <pt><ph keyref="FIT_MODE_COVER_POSITION"/></pt>
                <pd>Use the <parmname>positionInLandscapeMode</parmname> and <parmname>positionInPortraitMode</parmname> values you set in <xref keyref="WatermarkOptions"/>. The settings in <xref keyref="WatermarkRatio"/> are invalid.</pd>
            </plentry>
            <plentry>
                <pt><ph keyref="FIT_MODE_USE_IMAGE_RATIO"/></pt>
                <pd>Use the value you set in <xref keyref="WatermarkRatio"/>. The settings in <parmname>positionInLandscapeMode</parmname> and <parmname>positionInPortraitMode</parmname> in <xref keyref="WatermarkOptions"/> are invalid.</pd>
            </plentry>
            </parml> </section>
    </refbody>
</reference>
